                           <p>Incomplete at the beginning and at the end.</p>
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>Parchment damaged by damp.
</p>
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>Tidemarks at edges.</p>
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>Losses to rodents at top corner, general dirt and stains.</p>
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>Occasional mould spotting.</p>
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>Some losses of text due to old repairs.</p>
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>Folio 214 preserved only partially.</p>
                        
                        
                        
                        </condition>
                     
                     
                     
